Works great. I have an android phone and have run several speed tests on multiple internet service. Results are comparable to a speed test run on gigabit ethernet on a computer

I work outside during the winter and this hat is perfect. I have a big head and the hat is fairly big even for me. That being said it was exactly what I needed. Since I sweat a lot while working, I need to wash my hats more often. Most hats tend to shrink dramatically after numerous runs through the dryer which become unwearable for me. It's been one full winter and this hat seems like it will be useable for several more to come
Easy to install. Fit my 43' tv perfectly. Strong durable parts
This code reader did exactly what I needed it to do. It gave me the code for the check engine light on my dash with a description of the code. Also cleared the code when fixed

Works well. Like any properly fitting brace I have purchased, it was a little tight the first time I wore it but it did break in nicely after multiple uses. I use it to play basketball in a pick up league. It helps limit the motion on my shooting arm (elbow) which I fractured many years ago. I would buy this product again if needed in the future
